00:34:45.780 --> 00:34:49.159
Now as you start building
your own VR experiences

00:34:49.159 --> 00:34:51.739
from your rough ideas
to finished products,

00:34:51.739 --> 00:34:55.480
one thing you will need for
sure is a strong design team.

00:34:55.480 --> 00:34:59.130
My name is Anshuman Kumar,
and I'm a design lead

00:34:59.130 --> 00:35:00.040
on the Daydream team.

00:35:00.040 --> 00:35:03.320
And I'm going to be talking
about building VR design teams.

00:35:03.320 --> 00:35:05.330
And for the designers
in the audience

00:35:05.330 --> 00:35:07.500
and those watching
it online, if you

00:35:07.500 --> 00:35:10.507
want to start designing for VR,
towards the end of my session,

00:35:10.507 --> 00:35:12.090
I'm going to be
